maravilloso lo que hiciste por Norma

47:32.060 --> 47:34.145
¿No se que haría ella sin tí?

47:34.880 --> 47:36.964
No se que haría yo sin ella

47:38.352 --> 47:39.395
en realidad no lo sé

47:40.291 --> 47:41.334
El regalo perfecto

47:41.335 --> 47:42.378
gracias

47:42.379 --> 47:43.422
gracias a ti

47:44.733 --> 47:49.113
<i>Do you want to see me crawl
across the floor to you? </i>

47:51.314 --> 47:54.442
<i>Do you want to hear me beg you
to take me back? </i>

47:56.138 --> 48:03.020
<i>I'd gladly do it because
I don't want to fade away.</i>

48:03.021 --> 48:06.150
<i>Give me one more day, please.</i>

48:06.151 --> 48:15.536
<i>I don't want to fade away.
In your heart I want to stay.</i>

